Users API Roles We should also add our role-based authorization middleware to our /api/v1/users routes. This can actually be done really simply, because we only want users with the manage_users role to be able to access any of these routes.
So, instead of attaching the middleware to each handler individually, we can attach it directly to the router before any handlers:
